		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_STANNARY_HELP">
			<Text>+15% [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production when building Land Units in this City. Each source of  [ICON_RES_IRON] Iron and [ICON_RES_COPPER] Copper worked by this City produces +3 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production. Only the Celts may build it.</Text>
